<title>USA: HE-RO Group ends talks about sale.</title>
<headline>HE-RO Group ends talks about sale.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-01-15</dateline>
<text>
<p>HE-RO Group Ltd said on Wednesday that it has ended negotiations and its agreement with an affiliate of Sun Capital Partners Inc, a merchant banking and investment banking firm, about the sale of a controlling stake of the company.</p>
<p>The company is currently conducting negotiations with another potential purchaser, HE-RO said.</p>
